						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged and incomplete. Seems to refer to a gift of land after purchase for fifteen <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold by an individual Muttipperumāṉār, for <hi rend="italic">bhaṭṭavṛitti</hi> (for the maintenance of the brāhmaṇas who expound vēdas). Other details are not clear.</p>						

